---
title: Garlic Breadcrumb-Topped Salmon with Potato Coins and Snap Peas
description: Rich garlic spread and crunchy panko combine to make a golden, crisp topping for tender salmon! Dunk every bite into cooling yogurt sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-et-garniture-chapelure-ail-936751e7.jpg
